profile.bio: Ass. Professor, Harvard University. UCLA; Meraki, Inc. (now Cisco); Mazu Networks (now Riverbed). Click, Gifsicle, HotCRP, lcdf-typetools, t1utils, a mah jongg solitaire game you can play on Virgin America seatbacks.
